AuthorName: Danielle Woro Prabandari
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: "When traveling, i discover a new place, embrace new experiences in every aspects.\
  \ I tried not to visit the touristic place, I\u2019m looking for the most authentic,\
  \ the most unique things on my vosit. The street, the nature It\u2019s view, meeting\
  \ new people. Oh and the food. The Taste, feelings, and  sight bring memories l,\
  \ when your senses work better than a camera. Visiting non touristic place also\
  \ rediscover myself. From the pictures i realized that I\u2019m not a selfie person.\
  \ I love architecture, culture, food, and people. I love beautiful colors, and diversity.\
  \ \nIn Portugal i will visit places that has history and connected to my country\u2019\
  s history back then. Somehow i feel conected with Portugal, the words, the food\
  \ , the music in Indonesia that have influence from Portuguese culture. It\u2019\
  s like a reminiscence journey that marks indonesian History and also my history.\
  \ It\u2019s going to be an important travel for me at some point. The enticing journey,\
  \ a time travel, yet new experience."
